INSERT INTO `wpag_postmeta` VALUES('879', '291', 'section_4_content', 'Gone are the days of \"roll your own\" stream processing. AgilData is the simplest way for enterprises to leverage Big Data without having to become experts in a complex and changing toolset.\r\n\r\nOnly an Agile approach can rapidly accelerate the pace of product development while simplifying operations. AgilData brings this to your data infrastructure, leveraging four fundamental concepts. An Agile Big Data Infrastructure must be Simple, Scalable, Streaming and most importantly, must be SQL.');
